</span>, in the <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_domain" ti=
tle=3D"Time domain">time domain</a></i>) to a function of a <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complex_number" title=3D"Complex number">complex =
variable</a> <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span=
 class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: no=
