</p><p>The transform is useful for converting <a href=3D"https://en.wikiped=
ia.org/wiki/Derivative" title=3D"Derivative">differentiation</a> and <a hre=
f=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integral" title=3D"Integral">integration=
</a> in the time domain into much easier <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
g/wiki/Multiplication" title=3D"Multiplication">multiplication</a> and <a h=
ref=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Division_(mathematics)" title=3D"Divis=
ion (mathematics)">division</a> in the Laplace domain (analogous to how <a =
