s)=3D\int _{-\infty }^{\infty }e^{-st}f(t)\,dt.}"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
(<span id=3D"math_Eq._2" class=3D"reference nourlexpansion" style=3D"font-w=
eight:bold;">Eq. 2</span>)
</p>
</div>
<p>An alternate notation for the bilateral Laplace transform is <span class=
