<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Algebraic_construction">Alg=
ebraic construction</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-ed=
itsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?=
title=3DLaplace_transform&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D6" title=3D"Edit =
section: Algebraic construction"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-edi=
tsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The Laplace transform can be alternatively defined in a purely algebraic=
 manner by applying a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Field_of_fra=
ctions" title=3D"Field of fractions">field of fractions</a> construction to=
