section-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?ti=
tle=3DLaplace_transform&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D7" title=3D"Edit se=
ction: Region of convergence"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editse=
ction-bracket">]</span></span></div>
