ce"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laplace_transform#cite_note-27=
"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>27<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</sp=
an></a></sup> If  <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>a</i>(<i>n</i>)</span> is a di=
screte function of a positive integer <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>n</i></spa=
n>, then the power series associated to <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>a</i>(<i=
