{0^{-}}^{\infty }e^{-st}f(t)\,dt\\[6pt]&amp;=3D\left[{\frac {f(t)e^{-st}}{-=
s}}\right]_{0^{-}}^{\infty }-\int _{0^{-}}^{\infty }{\frac {e^{-st}}{-s}}f'=
(t)\,dt\quad {\text{(by parts)}}\\[6pt]&amp;=3D\left[-{\frac {f(0^{-})}{-s}=
}\right]+{\frac {1}{s}}{\mathcal {L}}\left\{f'(t)\right\},\end{aligned}}}">
