Then the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limit_of_a_function" titl=
e=3D"Limit of a function">limit</a> as <i>x</i> goes to infinity of <i>e</i=
><sup>=E2=88=92<i>x</i></sup>=E2=80=89<i>A</i>(<i>x</i>) is equal to&nbsp;c=
.
</p><p>This statement can be applied in particular to the <a href=3D"https:=
//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithmic_derivative" title=3D"Logarithmic deriva=
