i/Riemann_zeta_function" title=3D"Riemann zeta function">Riemann zeta funct=
ion</a>, and thus provides an extremely short way to prove the <a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prime_number_theorem" title=3D"Prime number th=
eorem">prime number theorem</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-44" class=3D"reference"=
